"酒店\">酒店<a title=\"#酒店\" href=\"#酒店\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"澜亭禧悦酒店\">澜亭禧悦酒店<a title=\"#澜亭禧悦酒店\" href=\"#澜亭禧悦酒店\"></a></h3>\n<p>地点：扬州市广陵区南通东路南下河112号<br>\n评分：★★★★</p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/yangzhou/hotel_01.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/yangzhou/hotel_02.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"美食\">美食<a title=\"#美食\" href=\"#美食\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"冶春茶社（早茶）\">冶春茶社（早茶）<a title=\"#冶春茶社（早茶）\" href=\"#冶春茶社（早茶）\"></a></h3>\n<p>推荐五丁包，大煮干丝，蟹黄汤包</p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/yangzhou/yechunchashe_01.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/yangzhou/yechunchashe_02.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/yangzhou/yechunchashe_03.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"流年渡（下午茶）\">流年渡（下午茶）<a title=\"#流年渡（下午茶）\" href=\"#流年渡（下午茶）\"></a></h3>\n<p>在东关街里面，环境优美，门口有一只可爱的小猫 ~</p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/yangzhou/liuliandu_01.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/yangzhou/liuliandu_02.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/yangzhou/liuliandu_03.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/yangzhou/liuliandu_04.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/yangzhou/liuliandu_05.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"景点\">景点<a title=\"#景点\" href=\"#景点\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"瘦西湖\">瘦西湖<a title=\"#瘦西湖\" href=\"#瘦西湖\"></a></h3>\n<p>今天运气不错，本来天气预报说有雨但是没下下来。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/yangzhou/shouxihu_01.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/yangzhou/shouxihu_02.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/yangzhou/shouxihu_03.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/yangzhou/shouxihu_04.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/yangzhou/shouxihu_05.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/yangzhou/shouxihu_06.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/yangzhou/shouxihu_07.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/yangzhou/shouxihu_08.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"东关街\">东关街<a title=\"#东关街\" href=\"#东关街\"></a></h3>\n<p>东关街是扬州最具有代表性的一条历史老街，有点类似南京夫子庙，里面有很多小吃。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/yangzhou/dongguanjie_01.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/yangzhou/dongguanjie_02.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/yangzhou/dongguanjie_03.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/yangzhou/dongguanjie_04.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/yangzhou/dongguanjie_05.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"感悟\">感悟<a title=\"#感悟\" href=\"#感悟\"></a></h2>\n<p>第一次跟淼淼出来旅游，在扬州留下了一段美好的回忆，以后要经常出来玩，爱你呦 ~</p>\n","prev":{"title":"【旅行】常州天目湖二日游","link":"2020/08/22/20200823_travel_changzhou"},"next":{"title":"写在前面","link":"2020/07/11/20200711_foreword"},"plink":"https://shome.love/2020/07/11/20200711_travel_yangzhou/","toc":[{"id":"规划","title":"规划","index":"1","children":[{"id":"时间","title":"时间","index":"1.1"},{"id":"路线","title":"路线","index":"1.2"}]},{"id":"车票","title":"车票","index":"2","children":[{"id":"南京站-→-扬州站","title":"南京站 → 扬州站","index":"2.1"}]},{"id":"酒店","title":"酒店","index":"3","children":[{"id":"澜亭禧悦酒店","title":"澜亭禧悦酒店","index":"3.1"}]},{"id":"美食","title":"美食","index":"4","children":[{"id":"冶春茶社（早茶）","title":"冶春茶社（早茶）","index":"4.1"},{"id":"流年渡（下午茶）","title":"流年渡（下午茶）","index":"4.2"}]},{"id":"景点","title":"景点","index":"5","children":[{"id":"瘦西湖","title":"瘦西湖","index":"5.1"},{"id":"东关街","title":"东关街","index":"5.2"}]},{"id":"感悟","title":"感悟","index":"6"}]}